 of Whittaker integral identities\nconjectured by Bump (1989) and Bump and Friedberg (1990) and proved by Stade\n(2001, 2002). Our approach leads to new `combinatorial' proofs and\ngeneralizations of these identities, with some restrictions on the parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Oct 2012 13:57:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Jun 2013 12:52:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-30"}
